EDIT → STAGE → COMMIT → PUSH → GITHUB PAGES LIVE

# check current repo status (what changed, what is untracked)
git status

# stage all changes (prepare files for saving)
git add .

# save snapshot of changes with message
git commit -m "your message here"

# upload local commits to GitHub (updates website)
git push origin main

# get latest changes from GitHub (if repo updated elsewhere)
git pull

